WEBVTT

01:26.440 --> 01:35.020
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.380 --> 01:37.910
[Episode 7]

01:41.840 --> 01:43.440
It's almost ready, Zongbao.

01:43.539 --> 01:44.560
Dish it up.

01:44.930 --> 01:46.250
Dish up what?

01:46.430 --> 01:47.509
Making sauce

01:48.150 --> 01:49.259
takes patience.

01:49.289 --> 01:50.620
It smells good enough.

01:50.620 --> 01:51.950
I can't wait any longer.

01:54.350 --> 01:55.550
Ranran, you're back.

01:57.340 --> 01:58.470
Why are you so happy?

01:58.700 --> 02:00.060
Look at that smile.

02:00.310 --> 02:01.590
Something good must have happened.

02:01.590 --> 02:02.130
Yes.

02:02.200 --> 02:04.060
I'm going to meet a director soon.

02:05.650 --> 02:07.060
That's great news.

02:07.180 --> 02:08.190
Don't get too excited.

02:08.190 --> 02:09.680
It's just the first step.

02:09.740 --> 02:11.270
I need to make it a solid one.

02:12.080 --> 02:13.370
That's the right attitude.

02:13.370 --> 02:14.870
I wouldn't get excited for anyone else.

02:14.870 --> 02:16.920
But for you, I'm thrilled.

02:17.000 --> 02:17.980
Look at you.

02:18.180 --> 02:20.010
Ranran has improved.

02:20.300 --> 02:21.360
She certainly has.

02:21.360 --> 02:22.360
Her Mandarin

02:22.360 --> 02:23.710
is getting better and better.

02:23.710 --> 02:25.240
With you guys backing me,

02:25.340 --> 02:26.750
it's hard not to improve.

02:28.060 --> 02:29.060
What are we eating today?

02:29.060 --> 02:29.810
Noodles with fried bean sauce.

02:29.810 --> 02:30.690
Is there any for me?

02:30.690 --> 02:31.800
-Yes.
-Yes.

02:31.800 --> 02:32.340
Great.

02:32.470 --> 02:33.000
Ranran.

02:33.560 --> 02:34.520
Let me tell you.

02:35.020 --> 02:36.180
When meeting a director,

02:36.180 --> 02:37.570
you should bring a gift.

02:37.680 --> 02:39.410
One can never be too courteous.

02:39.840 --> 02:41.630
I was just about to mention that.

02:41.630 --> 02:42.590
I heard that the director

02:42.590 --> 02:43.520
loves drinking.

02:43.680 --> 02:45.400
But I know nothing about liquor.

02:45.400 --> 02:46.810
What liquor should I buy?

02:46.960 --> 02:48.160
Fenjiu, definitely.

02:48.210 --> 02:48.940
From Shanxi.

02:49.120 --> 02:49.690
Fenjiu?

02:49.960 --> 02:51.910
If you must bring something, bring the best.

02:51.910 --> 02:52.590
Maotai.

02:52.690 --> 02:53.170
Maotai.

02:53.520 --> 02:54.380
Maotai is good.

02:54.960 --> 02:56.280
M-Maotai?

02:56.400 --> 02:57.460
How much is Maotai?

02:57.500 --> 02:58.560
Probably...

02:58.780 --> 03:00.300
One or two hundred a bottle.

03:00.300 --> 03:01.500
That's so expensive.

03:03.120 --> 03:04.740
Forget it. For art.

03:05.000 --> 03:05.660
I'll buy it.

03:05.970 --> 03:06.520
But...

03:06.800 --> 03:08.660
When are you seeing the director?

03:08.870 --> 03:09.470
Tomorrow.

03:10.180 --> 03:11.240
It's too late then.

03:11.810 --> 03:13.410
The shops are all closed now.

03:13.740 --> 03:14.130
Ranran,

03:14.130 --> 03:16.329
you want to buy Maotai for the director?

03:17.210 --> 03:18.500
Do you have a connection?

03:18.500 --> 03:20.360
I don't have a connection, but...

03:20.650 --> 03:21.579
I have 2 bottles.

03:22.360 --> 03:23.470
Stop bragging.

03:23.470 --> 03:24.750
-You have 2 bottles?
-Hold these for me.

03:24.750 --> 03:25.400
Do you have 2 bottles of liquor,

03:25.400 --> 03:26.730
or just 2 empty bottles?

03:27.410 --> 03:28.470
He doesn't even drink.

03:28.470 --> 03:29.870
Why would he have Maotai?

03:32.210 --> 03:33.410
What are these, then?

03:35.060 --> 03:35.460
What are these?

03:35.460 --> 03:35.860
You really have them?

03:35.860 --> 03:36.780
You really do.

03:36.930 --> 03:38.030
I was saving them

03:38.079 --> 03:39.650
to give them to the director, too.

03:39.650 --> 03:40.970
But you're seeing him tomorrow.

03:40.970 --> 03:42.230
So you take them first.

03:42.310 --> 03:42.800
Right.

03:43.090 --> 03:44.060
With your tolerance,

03:44.060 --> 03:46.180
no one would believe they're yours anyway.

03:46.180 --> 03:47.690
Such expensive liquors...

03:47.690 --> 03:49.190
And you're just giving them away?

03:49.190 --> 03:50.180
I'm lending them to her.

03:50.180 --> 03:51.840
If you're going to give a gift,

03:51.840 --> 03:52.560
then...

03:52.560 --> 03:54.090
You have to make it count.

03:54.130 --> 03:55.460
You can't skimp on this.

03:56.240 --> 03:57.050
Mr. Xu,

03:57.360 --> 03:58.180
thank you.

03:58.780 --> 03:59.560
When I get paid,

03:59.560 --> 04:00.900
I'll pay you back immediately.

04:00.900 --> 04:01.500
It's fine.

04:01.870 --> 04:03.430
I'll put in a good word with Zhuang Zhuang

04:03.430 --> 04:04.190
for you.

04:05.210 --> 04:06.080
No need.

04:06.530 --> 04:06.990
Ranran.

04:07.210 --> 04:08.500
If this works out,

04:08.500 --> 04:09.530
what do you want to eat?

04:09.530 --> 04:10.530
I'll make it for you.

04:10.530 --> 04:12.410
These noodles with fried bean sauce
smell great.

04:12.410 --> 04:14.090
Zongbao just finished cooking them
with my guidance.

04:14.090 --> 04:14.620
Let's go.

04:14.740 --> 04:15.780
Let's set up the table.

04:15.780 --> 04:16.779
Let's go, Ranran.

04:16.950 --> 04:18.860
With your guidance?

04:19.060 --> 04:20.390
I simmered it for 20 minutes.

04:20.390 --> 04:21.320
What a braggart.

04:23.180 --> 04:23.750
Zongbao.

04:24.330 --> 04:26.240
Add less sugar next time.

04:28.720 --> 04:29.850
Let's not go inside.

04:30.010 --> 04:31.840
The 3 of us will eat here.

04:32.310 --> 04:32.770
Okay.

04:33.060 --> 04:34.659
I'll get the noodles for you.

04:37.890 --> 04:38.350
Zhuang.

04:38.740 --> 04:39.980
No, my loyal subject.

04:40.190 --> 04:43.000
I grant you ten thousand taels of gold

04:43.360 --> 04:45.450
and several fine horses.

04:46.010 --> 04:47.270
You're unbelievable.

04:47.930 --> 04:48.390
Zhuang.

04:48.480 --> 04:49.610
Come here, quickly.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.100
Look at me.

04:51.240 --> 04:52.240
Who do I look like?

04:53.250 --> 04:54.159
Wu Zetian?

04:54.360 --> 04:56.550
Zhuang, how did you guess it?

04:56.810 --> 04:58.210
Your acting was on point.

04:58.600 --> 04:59.690
-Have you chosen the clothes?
-Of course.

04:59.690 --> 05:00.740
I think every piece

05:00.740 --> 05:01.470
looks great.

05:01.680 --> 05:03.280
Every piece looks beautiful

05:03.300 --> 05:04.930
on me.

05:06.420 --> 05:07.280
Servant,

05:07.740 --> 05:09.670
pass down my command immediately.

05:09.720 --> 05:12.300
Serve the Imperial Feast.

05:15.190 --> 05:15.570
Here.

05:16.600 --> 05:18.860
Alright, Your Highness. Time to change.

05:19.680 --> 05:20.950
Look at you, so happy.

05:22.070 --> 05:22.630
Zhuang.

05:23.310 --> 05:24.510
Right now,

05:24.600 --> 05:26.560
I feel so happy.

05:27.190 --> 05:28.070
Be careful.

05:28.750 --> 05:30.030
It's good to be happy.

05:30.190 --> 05:31.040
From now on, happy things

05:31.040 --> 05:32.170
will only increase.

05:33.370 --> 05:33.860
Look.

05:35.300 --> 05:37.300
Which one do you think looks better?

05:37.630 --> 05:38.500
The yellow one.

05:38.770 --> 05:41.060
It matches your hair accessory perfectly.

05:41.060 --> 05:42.070
I think so too.

05:42.130 --> 05:43.659
I'll listen to you, Zhuang.

05:44.800 --> 05:45.260
Come on.

05:52.510 --> 05:54.190
Wait a second. I'm almost done.

05:54.190 --> 05:55.320
Working hard, I see.

06:07.860 --> 06:09.660
I heard that you did someone

06:09.660 --> 06:11.190
a favor again today, Mr. Xu.

06:13.220 --> 06:15.190
Meeting the director is a big deal.

06:15.540 --> 06:16.570
I really hope that

06:16.570 --> 06:17.700
Ranran can succeed.

06:17.870 --> 06:19.200
You empathize with her.

06:21.800 --> 06:23.000
Something like that.

06:25.450 --> 06:27.510
Director Weng will be back soon, too.

06:31.180 --> 06:32.650
I had a fight with him.

06:32.770 --> 06:34.560
Do you think it'll affect things?

06:34.560 --> 06:36.480
After a hurricane comes the rainbow.

06:36.480 --> 06:37.340
Don't you know?

06:39.800 --> 06:40.550
Yes.

06:41.190 --> 06:43.540
After a hurricane comes the rainbow.

06:47.070 --> 06:48.670
The simplest kind of support

06:49.000 --> 06:50.530
seems to be the most useful.

06:55.040 --> 06:55.480
Yeah.

06:56.510 --> 06:58.690
The simplest support works best.

06:59.630 --> 07:01.430
Earning money with you

07:01.480 --> 07:02.620
for the long haul

07:02.980 --> 07:04.110
is pretty good, too.

07:11.240 --> 07:12.300
Hurry up and write.

07:13.570 --> 07:14.540
I just finished a section.

07:14.540 --> 07:15.940
Why don't you take a look?

07:16.620 --> 07:18.510
Will I even understand your script?

07:18.510 --> 07:19.630
What's there not to understand?

07:19.630 --> 07:20.600
It's just a story.

07:20.600 --> 07:21.260
Take a look.

07:21.980 --> 07:22.590
Alright.

07:25.980 --> 07:27.040
Nice handwriting.

07:27.130 --> 07:27.890
What does that mean?

07:27.890 --> 07:29.130
Is the content not good?

07:29.130 --> 07:29.810
Be quiet.

07:44.670 --> 07:46.790
[Welcome "Outsider" Crew To Our Hotel]

07:47.620 --> 07:50.480
["Outsider" Production Team]

07:50.510 --> 07:53.980
[Director's Studio]

07:52.180 --> 07:52.740
Coming.

07:54.740 --> 07:55.159
You're here.

07:55.159 --> 07:56.000
Quick, come in.

07:56.000 --> 07:56.420
Okay.

07:56.810 --> 07:57.360
Come on.

07:57.220 --> 08:01.590
[Prop cars] [Prop IDs]

07:58.390 --> 07:59.120
Director Ma.

07:59.480 --> 08:00.930
This is the person I mentioned to you,

08:00.930 --> 08:01.660
Shen Ranran.

08:02.720 --> 08:03.430
Director!

08:03.540 --> 08:04.190
Director!

08:04.360 --> 08:05.690
Your hands are made for directing.

08:04.970 --> 08:10.050
[Character settings]

08:05.800 --> 08:06.420
Let me do it.

08:06.420 --> 08:07.550
Please, have a seat.

08:08.480 --> 08:09.600
Director, well.

08:10.240 --> 08:11.920
Ranran is from Huzhou.

08:11.950 --> 08:13.410
Her acting is pretty good.

08:14.580 --> 08:16.060
Just because you say so?

08:17.680 --> 08:18.280
Director.

08:18.430 --> 08:19.530
I talk too much.

08:19.660 --> 08:20.590
You be the judge.

08:22.510 --> 08:23.240
Director Ma.

08:23.480 --> 08:24.750
Mr. Cui asked me to come here.

08:24.750 --> 08:25.870
It's my first time meeting you.

08:25.870 --> 08:27.240
I didn't know what to bring.

08:27.240 --> 08:29.000
I just bought 2 bottles of good liquor

08:29.000 --> 08:29.800
for you to try.

08:29.810 --> 08:31.070
Please look out for me.

08:31.680 --> 08:32.940
That's so thoughtful.

08:33.700 --> 08:34.370
Well...

08:34.600 --> 08:35.630
Director.

08:36.720 --> 08:38.080
Wine and meat just pass through us.

08:38.080 --> 08:38.940
It's harmless.

08:40.480 --> 08:42.150
This liquor makes our food

08:42.150 --> 08:42.960
look lacking.

08:43.370 --> 08:45.150
Shall I go buy a few more dishes?

08:45.910 --> 08:46.970
Why are you asking?

08:46.980 --> 08:47.910
I'll go with you.

08:48.060 --> 08:49.520
[Character settings]

08:53.200 --> 08:54.530
Let me tell you, Ranran.

08:54.650 --> 08:55.850
These 4 dishes

08:55.980 --> 08:57.840
have been blessed by Director Ma's aura.

08:57.840 --> 08:59.670
Even the finest delicacies can't compare.

08:59.670 --> 09:00.630
You and your mouth.

09:00.630 --> 09:02.720
Keep talking, and the food will get cold.

09:02.720 --> 09:03.720
Come, have a seat.

09:04.060 --> 09:05.390
Thank you, Director Ma.

09:05.520 --> 09:14.750
[Character settings]

09:06.290 --> 09:06.720
Director.

09:06.720 --> 09:07.920
I'll use the teacups.

09:08.010 --> 09:08.340
Okay.

09:09.820 --> 09:10.130
Here.

09:10.130 --> 09:11.460
Thank you, Director Ma.

09:12.990 --> 09:13.650
Let me do it.

09:13.670 --> 09:14.670
Let me, Director.

09:17.980 --> 09:18.710
Director Ma,

09:19.360 --> 09:20.020
have a look.

09:24.320 --> 09:25.450
You shouldn't have.

09:37.030 --> 09:37.460
Director.

09:37.460 --> 09:38.630
Let me pour it.

09:38.770 --> 09:39.440
Here.

09:40.000 --> 09:40.370
Okay.

09:46.630 --> 09:47.010
Here.

09:53.250 --> 09:54.150
Thank you, Mr. Cui.

09:54.150 --> 09:54.600
Here.

10:00.550 --> 10:01.280
Director Ma.

10:02.440 --> 10:04.840
Ranran and I would like to offer you a toast.

10:05.530 --> 10:06.240
Okay.

10:06.630 --> 10:08.560
Wish you good health, Director Ma.

10:08.620 --> 10:09.500
May you create more great titles

10:09.500 --> 10:10.630
and win more awards.

10:11.460 --> 10:12.660
Thank you.

10:13.170 --> 10:13.890
She has a way with words.

10:13.790 --> 10:16.060
[Prop IDs]

10:13.890 --> 10:15.090
Even better than you.

10:32.080 --> 10:32.740
Young lady,

10:33.980 --> 10:35.970
I noticed when you drank just now,

10:36.250 --> 10:38.200
you frowned a little.

10:38.960 --> 10:39.760
What's wrong?

10:40.250 --> 10:40.720
I...

10:41.250 --> 10:43.180
I've never had this liquor before.

10:43.370 --> 10:44.430
It's quite strong.

10:50.700 --> 10:51.780
Good liquor

10:52.860 --> 10:53.910
is always strong.

10:56.360 --> 10:57.420
It's getting cold.

10:57.550 --> 10:58.980
Come on, eat up.

10:59.150 --> 10:59.580
Have some food.

10:59.580 --> 10:59.940
Okay.

11:00.080 --> 11:01.340
It's all getting cold.

11:02.220 --> 11:03.950
Come on. Make yourself at home.

11:04.840 --> 11:06.080
Come on.

11:08.090 --> 11:11.830
[Welcome "Outsider" Crew To Our Hotel]

11:08.220 --> 11:08.890
Mr. Cui.

11:09.500 --> 11:10.050
Mr. Cui.

11:10.550 --> 11:11.770
Mr. Cui.

11:12.340 --> 11:14.140
Isn't Director Ma a big drinker?

11:14.270 --> 11:15.870
Why did he only drink 1 cup?

11:16.100 --> 11:17.930
Did he not like the liquor?

11:18.050 --> 11:19.780
Or was it too precious to drink?

11:21.240 --> 11:22.510
Probably too precious.

11:22.510 --> 11:22.960
So,

11:23.970 --> 11:25.590
what does he think of me?

11:25.790 --> 11:26.790
What do you think?

11:26.910 --> 11:28.080
I don't know.

11:28.080 --> 11:29.130
During the meal,

11:29.130 --> 11:30.260
he didn't say a word.

11:30.580 --> 11:31.740
I didn't dare to ask.

11:32.170 --> 11:32.750
I know.

11:34.440 --> 11:35.370
You're done for.

11:38.320 --> 11:40.040
Don't you get it, Ranran?

11:40.370 --> 11:41.820
The liquor you brought was blended.

11:41.820 --> 11:43.040
It wasn't authentic.

11:43.170 --> 11:44.170
That's impossible.

11:44.170 --> 11:45.150
Why is it impossible?

11:45.150 --> 11:46.200
Director Ma is a connoisseur.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.010
He's had every kind of liquor.

11:47.010 --> 11:48.600
Even I could taste that it was fake.

11:48.600 --> 11:50.080
But Director Ma drank a cup.

11:50.080 --> 11:51.280
He didn't spit it out.

11:52.360 --> 11:53.960
You expect him to spit it out?

11:54.250 --> 11:55.740
Why are you so naive?

11:56.120 --> 11:56.750
I told you,

11:56.750 --> 11:57.820
he is a director.

11:58.550 --> 12:00.010
He was being considerate.

12:01.150 --> 12:02.200
Anyway,

12:02.870 --> 12:04.270
it's probably hopeless.

12:09.320 --> 12:11.120
That bottle cap had been opened.

12:11.510 --> 12:12.740
Most likely,

12:12.860 --> 12:14.990
they definitely gave you fake liquor.

12:15.200 --> 12:15.790
Impossible.

12:15.790 --> 12:16.940
They aren't like that.

12:16.940 --> 12:18.390
Who isn't like that?

12:19.120 --> 12:20.580
You're too naive, Ranran.

12:21.010 --> 12:21.360
I...

12:22.530 --> 12:23.170
Do you remember what Director Ma

12:23.170 --> 12:24.000
said to you?

12:24.270 --> 12:25.000
He told you to manage

12:25.000 --> 12:26.290
your interpersonal relationships.

12:26.290 --> 12:27.550
That was a warning.

12:27.960 --> 12:29.120
This... Then...

12:30.630 --> 12:31.230
Then...

12:31.460 --> 12:32.350
Then this time,

12:33.000 --> 12:35.120
do I have no chance?

12:35.460 --> 12:35.940
Well...

12:37.200 --> 12:38.010
Don't cry.

12:38.390 --> 12:39.640
Listen,

12:39.740 --> 12:41.400
the role hasn't been cast yet.

12:41.530 --> 12:43.660
So there might still be a spark of hope.

12:43.720 --> 12:45.720
No, I can't be left with just a spark.

12:45.870 --> 12:46.670
You have to help me.

12:46.670 --> 12:48.320
We need to stoke the fire.

12:48.320 --> 12:48.940
How?

12:49.170 --> 12:50.430
Pour fake liquor on it?

12:53.170 --> 12:53.770
This...

12:54.010 --> 12:55.870
What am I supposed to do?

12:57.410 --> 12:57.980
I must find

12:57.980 --> 12:59.120
the culprit

12:59.940 --> 13:01.120
and clear my name.

13:06.270 --> 13:07.400
Where is Xu Shengli?

13:08.220 --> 13:08.750
Not here.

13:10.080 --> 13:11.340
What's wrong, Ranran?

13:12.410 --> 13:13.740
It smells like alcohol.

13:15.030 --> 13:16.600
None of you are getting away with this.

13:16.600 --> 13:17.400
What alcohol?

13:17.460 --> 13:18.390
Open your mouth.

13:19.220 --> 13:19.670
What do you mean?

13:19.670 --> 13:20.600
Open your mouth.

13:23.790 --> 13:24.840
I just ate garlic.

13:25.500 --> 13:26.430
Six cloves of it.

13:26.580 --> 13:27.510
You open up, too.

13:28.460 --> 13:28.860
Me?

13:33.300 --> 13:33.890
Come on.

13:33.890 --> 13:35.690
I... I just had some chili sauce.

13:36.870 --> 13:37.270
I...

13:38.700 --> 13:40.530
I just had stinky tofu.

13:42.510 --> 13:43.770
What's wrong, Ranran?

13:44.460 --> 13:46.390
Take your time and speak your mind.

13:46.790 --> 13:49.050
How did it go with Director Ma?

13:51.240 --> 13:53.100
The 2 bottles of liquor you gave me

13:53.120 --> 13:54.060
were fake.

13:54.240 --> 13:55.120
-What?
-What?

13:55.240 --> 13:55.700
What's going on?

13:55.700 --> 13:56.630
What? What liquor?

13:56.630 --> 13:57.050
What liquor?

13:57.050 --> 13:58.480
The 2 bottles Xu Shengli gave me

13:58.480 --> 13:59.580
were fake!

14:00.050 --> 14:01.580
I've offended the director

14:01.580 --> 14:02.860
and lost my chance at acting.

14:02.860 --> 14:03.440
My life has been ruined

14:03.440 --> 14:05.300
by those 2 bottles of fake liquor!

14:05.440 --> 14:06.010
I shouldn't have

14:06.010 --> 14:07.720
given those 2 bottles of liquor.

14:07.720 --> 14:09.700
Why are you trying to ruin it for me?

14:11.140 --> 14:12.800
You've completely ruined it!

14:14.580 --> 14:15.700
It's over.

14:16.480 --> 14:17.820
It's all over now.

14:18.390 --> 14:19.790
I offended the director.

14:19.960 --> 14:22.150
I'll never get another role.

14:22.500 --> 14:23.630
It can't be that bad.

14:24.820 --> 14:26.670
Forget it.

14:27.960 --> 14:29.760
No matter how nice my words were,

14:30.240 --> 14:31.720
I ended up giving fake liquor

14:31.720 --> 14:32.650
to the director.

14:32.870 --> 14:34.630
He... he must think

14:34.630 --> 14:36.240
I did it on purpose.

14:36.290 --> 14:38.000
You can't be blamed for this.

14:38.120 --> 14:39.920
Just explain it to the director.

14:44.500 --> 14:45.710
Did Xu Shengli

14:46.410 --> 14:47.580
do it on purpose?

14:48.600 --> 14:50.860
He's definitely not that kind of person.

14:52.750 --> 14:53.320
Zhuang,

14:54.270 --> 14:56.200
you're siding with him.

14:57.510 --> 14:58.240
Don't worry.

14:58.600 --> 15:01.000
I will definitely find the culprit for you.

15:01.840 --> 15:02.700
Zhuang Zhuang.

15:02.790 --> 15:04.130
Open the door.

15:04.370 --> 15:06.150
Ranran is still crying over there.

15:06.150 --> 15:07.370
She's crying her heart out.

15:07.370 --> 15:08.890
I feel terrible, too.

15:08.890 --> 15:10.550
Let me go over and comfort her.

15:11.500 --> 15:12.360
Zhuang Zhuang!

15:14.000 --> 15:15.200
Then help Mr. Guo out.

15:15.740 --> 15:17.120
He's getting on in years.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.270
He has prostate issues.

15:18.270 --> 15:19.860
He needs to use the bathroom.

15:19.860 --> 15:20.940
What are you doing?

15:20.940 --> 15:21.270
No...

15:22.100 --> 15:23.670
He can't hold it in anymore.

15:25.050 --> 15:26.150
Zhuang Zhuang.

15:26.940 --> 15:29.250
I can't hold it in anymore.

15:29.360 --> 15:30.690
Open the door, quickly.

15:32.270 --> 15:34.470
Zhuang Zhuang, I can't hold it anymore.

15:34.940 --> 15:36.710
What should I do?

15:37.120 --> 15:39.650
Should I pee in this bottle?

15:40.630 --> 15:41.670
It's too small.

15:43.290 --> 15:44.510
How about this one?

15:44.510 --> 15:45.370
Make do with it.

15:45.500 --> 15:47.150
You're crazy, Tao Liangliang.

15:47.150 --> 15:47.670
This works.

15:47.670 --> 15:48.600
This won't work.

15:48.620 --> 15:49.550
This is great.

15:49.550 --> 15:50.150
Open the door, quickly.

15:50.150 --> 15:50.840
Wait a minute, Zongbao.

15:50.840 --> 15:51.940
I'll find you something even

15:51.940 --> 15:52.980
more exciting.

15:54.030 --> 15:55.720
No, that's no good. No good.

15:55.750 --> 15:56.410
That won't do.

15:56.410 --> 15:57.460
What's wrong? Yours won't do,

15:57.460 --> 15:58.050
but mine is ok?

15:58.050 --> 15:58.550
No.

15:58.720 --> 16:00.580
This isn't exciting. Not exciting.

16:00.580 --> 16:02.200
It is. It's really exciting.

16:03.320 --> 16:04.180
Don't block me.

16:05.170 --> 16:06.050
Zhuang Zhuang.

16:06.250 --> 16:07.240
Open the door.

16:07.340 --> 16:08.800
I can't hold it in anymore.

16:08.820 --> 16:09.840
I'm dying here.

16:09.870 --> 16:11.290
Hurry up and open the door.

16:11.290 --> 16:13.220
Alright, stop shouting. It's useless.

16:13.220 --> 16:15.200
Useless or not, we can't just wait here.

16:15.200 --> 16:16.790
Why are you just standing here?

16:16.790 --> 16:17.990
I was waiting for you.

16:18.000 --> 16:18.800
What's wrong?

16:19.130 --> 16:20.460
It's about Shen Ranran.

16:21.170 --> 16:22.120
I told her

16:22.120 --> 16:23.850
there's no need to be so polite.

16:25.370 --> 16:26.380
I bought some food

16:26.600 --> 16:28.460
to thank everyone for their care.

16:28.620 --> 16:29.680
We'll eat and talk.

16:29.750 --> 16:30.680
Let's go inside.

16:42.720 --> 16:43.920
Oh, everyone's here.

16:44.460 --> 16:46.460
Zhuang Zhuang brought us some food.

16:46.960 --> 16:48.560
You finally opened the door.

16:52.130 --> 16:53.500
What are you doing?

16:54.130 --> 16:55.930
Give me a straight answer today.

16:56.240 --> 16:58.170
What happened to Ranran's liquor?

17:09.700 --> 17:10.430
Not talking?

17:11.720 --> 17:12.050
Fine.

17:12.920 --> 17:14.240
Then I'll torture you one by one.

17:14.240 --> 17:15.300
Starting with you.

17:15.460 --> 17:16.140
No, wait.

17:16.849 --> 17:17.310
What...

17:17.569 --> 17:18.970
What exactly is going on?

17:20.510 --> 17:22.710
The liquor you gave Shen Ranran is fake.

17:25.109 --> 17:25.980
Fake liquor?

17:27.569 --> 17:28.720
That's impossible.

17:29.000 --> 17:30.180
I bought it at the state-run store.

17:30.180 --> 17:31.240
I have the receipt.

17:39.710 --> 17:41.400
[Receipt]

17:46.450 --> 17:48.050
Could it have been switched?

17:48.440 --> 17:49.840
That's even less likely.

17:50.090 --> 17:51.240
The liquor was under my bed the whole time.

17:51.240 --> 17:52.300
I never took it out.

17:56.810 --> 17:58.000
Then the suspect must be

17:58.000 --> 17:58.800
from Room 108.

18:03.500 --> 18:04.450
What's going on?

18:07.530 --> 18:08.260
You go first.

18:11.200 --> 18:13.060
Then you should rule me out first.

18:13.830 --> 18:15.890
I bought the liquor for the director.

18:16.010 --> 18:17.330
So I'm a victim too.

18:17.500 --> 18:17.920
Right?

18:19.140 --> 18:20.040
Listen, Xu.

18:21.510 --> 18:23.380
You're just passing the buck

18:25.330 --> 18:26.990
and keeping your hands clean.

18:27.610 --> 18:28.590
Exactly.

18:29.000 --> 18:30.940
You share the weals but not the woes.

18:30.940 --> 18:31.880
How could you?

18:32.700 --> 18:34.000
What are you doing?

18:34.000 --> 18:35.650
We're all from the same room.

18:36.350 --> 18:38.070
At night, we all hear

18:38.510 --> 18:39.370
each other burp

18:39.400 --> 18:40.530
and grind our teeth.

18:40.680 --> 18:42.750
We even hear each other's sleep-talking.

18:42.750 --> 18:44.250
We keep an eye on each other, right?

18:44.250 --> 18:46.250
There are no bad people in this room.

18:47.950 --> 18:49.150
Your arm is on my hair.

18:52.680 --> 18:53.740
Who exactly did it?

18:54.010 --> 18:55.410
If it pertains to Ranran,

18:55.480 --> 18:57.680
it definitely couldn't have been me, right?

18:57.680 --> 18:58.830
It wasn't me either.

19:02.010 --> 19:03.410
Process of elimination?

19:04.160 --> 19:04.720
The one who walked in

19:04.720 --> 19:06.120
ruled himself out first.

19:06.330 --> 19:07.290
You said it pertained to Ranran,

19:07.290 --> 19:08.350
so it couldn't have been you,

19:08.350 --> 19:09.640
and absolutely not you.

19:09.640 --> 19:10.640
So that leaves me.

19:10.980 --> 19:11.330
Fine.

19:12.290 --> 19:13.750
You actually admitted it.

19:14.510 --> 19:15.940
Admit what?

19:15.940 --> 19:17.740
I was just joking.

19:17.790 --> 19:19.220
It's a good thing you aren't judges.

19:19.220 --> 19:20.070
Otherwise, so many people

19:20.070 --> 19:21.380
would have been wrongly executed.

19:21.380 --> 19:23.110
Bring out the guillotine.

19:23.380 --> 19:24.220
Exactly.

19:32.200 --> 19:33.660
Now you're joking around?

19:33.880 --> 19:34.900
No, we're not.

19:35.660 --> 19:36.570
Do you know how important

19:36.570 --> 19:37.990
this is to her?

19:38.440 --> 19:39.900
I'm telling you right now.

19:40.140 --> 19:41.830
Until we get to the bottom of this,

19:41.830 --> 19:43.360
no one is leaving this room.

19:43.720 --> 19:44.660
Think it over.

19:45.310 --> 19:47.110
It'll be too late once the police get here.

19:47.110 --> 19:47.570
Fine.

19:48.940 --> 19:50.560
Let's cut the crap.

19:50.610 --> 19:51.540
Call the police.

19:51.940 --> 19:52.880
Call them right now.

19:52.880 --> 19:53.440
No, no.

19:53.440 --> 19:53.940
Zongbao.

19:53.940 --> 19:56.470
No, no. The police will investigate me first.

19:56.740 --> 19:57.870
Investigate, then.

19:57.900 --> 19:59.360
We must investigate this.

19:59.570 --> 20:00.500
Call the police.

20:01.330 --> 20:03.210
We'll get to the bottom of this

20:03.380 --> 20:04.750
so I can beat the culprit up.

20:04.750 --> 20:06.280
We'll find out who did it...

20:07.270 --> 20:08.800
And teach him a good lesson.

20:08.810 --> 20:09.270
You...

20:09.270 --> 20:09.720
Investigate it!

20:09.720 --> 20:10.850
Where are you going?

20:10.940 --> 20:11.870
To the bathroom!

20:13.010 --> 20:13.870
Zhuang Zhuang.

20:14.510 --> 20:16.690
Go back and tell Ranran that

20:17.330 --> 20:19.560
she can leave this swapped liquor case

20:19.680 --> 20:20.380
to me.

20:20.640 --> 20:22.270
I will definitely

20:22.270 --> 20:23.930
get to the bottom of it for her.

20:26.880 --> 20:28.280
I'll go take a leak first.

20:30.750 --> 20:31.560
Don't worry.

20:32.200 --> 20:34.130
I said I'd help you investigate it,

20:34.660 --> 20:36.990
so I'll definitely get to the bottom of it.

20:44.390 --> 20:46.830
[Guest Room]

20:50.770 --> 20:51.870
Washing up?

21:02.070 --> 21:03.760
You already promised her.

21:03.790 --> 21:05.440
How do you plan to investigate?

21:05.440 --> 21:06.250
I...

21:06.830 --> 21:08.090
have figured out a way.

21:10.570 --> 21:12.100
You've figured it out, too?

21:15.070 --> 21:16.470
What are you grinning at?

21:20.350 --> 21:23.810
Others laugh at me for being too crazy,

21:24.700 --> 21:27.680
but I laugh at others
for not seeing through it.

21:28.610 --> 21:31.500
So... You have it in the bag?

21:33.460 --> 21:34.520
What are you doing?

21:36.550 --> 21:37.560
Do you suspect me?

21:41.000 --> 21:42.660
Have you ever had good liquor?

21:44.180 --> 21:45.380
Actually, I haven't.

21:45.640 --> 21:47.370
Then sniffing me is pointless.

21:48.460 --> 21:50.120
Even if it's a shot in the dark,

21:50.850 --> 21:52.580
I can always take a swing first.

21:52.810 --> 21:54.670
You're taking a swing at me first?

22:58.510 --> 22:59.380
What are you doing?

22:59.380 --> 23:00.580
What's going on?

23:00.920 --> 23:01.830
What's wrong?

23:03.380 --> 23:05.180
-What’s wrong?
-What happened?

23:06.530 --> 23:08.260
It's spicy!

23:08.640 --> 23:10.240
You liquor thief!

23:11.240 --> 23:13.010
What thief? Who's a thief?

23:13.720 --> 23:14.650
What's going on?

23:15.200 --> 23:16.600
Did you steal the liquor?

23:16.660 --> 23:17.390
What is this?

23:18.960 --> 23:20.180
Why is there a tube?

23:24.050 --> 23:25.180
What's this about?

23:29.920 --> 23:30.460
Sit down.

23:33.310 --> 23:36.000
Leniency for confession,
severity for resistance.

23:36.000 --> 23:36.420
Speak.

23:36.940 --> 23:38.200
You stole Xu's liquor,

23:38.960 --> 23:40.000
poured the real liquor into

23:40.000 --> 23:41.400
the bottle you prepared,

23:42.330 --> 23:43.790
and put the adulterated liquor

23:43.790 --> 23:45.520
back into the original bottle.

23:46.140 --> 23:46.870
Heretic Cao.

23:48.050 --> 23:50.540
You should change your name to Wicked Cao.

23:50.610 --> 23:51.000
I

23:51.000 --> 23:52.090
didn't know those 2 bottles

23:52.090 --> 23:54.290
were gifts before I tampered with them.

23:54.310 --> 23:56.050
I certainly didn't know they were for Ranran.

23:56.050 --> 23:56.450
You...

23:56.480 --> 23:58.080
The point is, think about it.

23:58.110 --> 23:59.420
With Xu Shengli's alcohol tolerance,

23:59.420 --> 24:00.720
isn't it a complete waste

24:00.720 --> 24:01.590
of good liquor

24:01.590 --> 24:03.610
for him to sleep on 2 bottles

24:03.770 --> 24:04.660
of fine liquor?

24:04.770 --> 24:05.770
If I had known earlier,

24:05.770 --> 24:07.830
I definitely wouldn't have drunk it.

24:07.880 --> 24:09.420
Why are you still making excuses?

24:09.420 --> 24:10.070
Look at you.

24:10.070 --> 24:11.480
You think you're in the right, don't you?

24:11.480 --> 24:12.680
Stay seated. You...

24:13.160 --> 24:13.590
You...

24:16.250 --> 24:17.510
You can steal anything

24:18.510 --> 24:19.290
but liquor.

24:19.720 --> 24:20.920
You're at fault.

24:21.570 --> 24:23.220
I am at fault.

24:24.420 --> 24:24.880
But...

24:25.400 --> 24:26.240
I... I just

24:26.240 --> 24:27.850
hadn't had good liquor before, okay?

24:27.850 --> 24:29.220
Since I saw it,

24:29.220 --> 24:30.820
how could I have resisted it?

24:31.330 --> 24:33.530
Yes, I admit that I've drunk the liquor.

24:33.850 --> 24:35.580
But I can't afford to pay for it.

24:35.940 --> 24:37.270
So... as for Ranran,

24:37.750 --> 24:38.880
if all else fails...

24:40.290 --> 24:41.090
My paintings.

24:41.090 --> 24:42.500
Look at all these paintings of mine.

24:42.500 --> 24:43.740
-Let Ranran pick one.
-Enough.

24:43.740 --> 24:44.380
If she doesn't like any of them,

24:44.380 --> 24:45.640
I can paint another one for her.

24:45.640 --> 24:47.200
She can give it to that director.

24:47.200 --> 24:48.310
Just tell the director that

24:48.310 --> 24:49.980
when Cao Ye becomes famous overnight,

24:49.980 --> 24:53.180
the painting will be worth
more than a bottle of liquor...

24:55.160 --> 24:55.980
Wait a minute.

24:56.460 --> 24:58.120
I didn't drink a whole bottle.

24:58.380 --> 25:00.330
I only drank less than half a bottle.

25:00.330 --> 25:01.310
Who swapped the rest

25:01.310 --> 25:02.380
with chili water?

25:04.310 --> 25:05.660
This is a separate matter.

25:05.660 --> 25:07.590
Is that something a human would do?

25:07.660 --> 25:09.500
Don't push your luck after getting off easy.

25:09.500 --> 25:11.000
I have other stuff here. You want some?

25:11.000 --> 25:12.330
That's enough from you.

25:13.790 --> 25:14.290
Xu.

25:14.900 --> 25:15.920
Say something.

25:25.750 --> 25:26.460
Xu Shengli.

25:27.000 --> 25:27.960
Is our feud

25:27.960 --> 25:29.010
ever going to end?

25:29.270 --> 25:31.330
I should be the one saying that to you.

25:35.750 --> 25:37.640
Where is the other bottle of liquor?

25:37.640 --> 25:38.480
I swear to God,

25:38.510 --> 25:39.640
I only took 1 bottle.

25:40.400 --> 25:42.110
So one bottle is authentic.

25:43.880 --> 25:45.540
Yes, one bottle is authentic.

25:45.570 --> 25:46.140
I'm not that kind of

25:46.140 --> 25:46.700
greedy person.

25:46.700 --> 25:47.240
Tomorrow morning,

25:47.240 --> 25:49.300
go apologize to Ranran immediately.

25:49.810 --> 25:50.610
I will, I will.

26:04.440 --> 26:06.170
We're just missing the liquor.

26:09.610 --> 26:11.470
Let me make my stance clear again.

26:11.660 --> 26:13.250
I will definitely apologize.

26:13.250 --> 26:14.590
But now that the liquor is poured out,

26:14.590 --> 26:15.980
it can't be poured back, can it?

26:15.980 --> 26:18.110
I'll have to pay for it sooner or later.

26:18.720 --> 26:20.050
One day, when I become famous,

26:20.050 --> 26:20.810
just one of my paintings

26:20.810 --> 26:22.610
will be worth 10 or 20 cases of it.

26:24.500 --> 26:24.900
I...

26:25.010 --> 26:25.420
I...

26:29.110 --> 26:29.570
This...

26:33.610 --> 26:34.480
This liquor

26:35.050 --> 26:35.910
smells so good.

26:36.240 --> 26:37.320
It really does.

26:37.830 --> 26:39.240
Ranran's liquor

26:39.640 --> 26:40.900
is for me only.

26:41.240 --> 26:43.100
I bought it. Let go.

26:46.880 --> 26:47.510
Let go!

26:49.380 --> 26:51.810
1, 2, 3.

26:54.110 --> 26:54.770
Go to sleep.

26:56.380 --> 26:57.960
Can you even sleep?

27:17.610 --> 27:18.380
Come take a look, Miss.

27:18.380 --> 27:19.710
Feel free to take a look.

27:28.900 --> 27:29.530
Ranran.

27:32.070 --> 27:33.790
What a small world.

27:33.900 --> 27:35.420
What are you doing here?

27:37.420 --> 27:38.740
Well, it's raining.

27:38.770 --> 27:40.940
I'm looking for inspiration here.

27:42.590 --> 27:43.460
Inspiration?

27:50.390 --> 27:52.770
Do you usually perform here?

27:55.110 --> 27:55.770
Perform...

27:57.290 --> 27:58.110
The performance, yes.

27:58.110 --> 27:59.530
The posters are up.

28:01.010 --> 28:02.340
"Carefree Wandering."

28:02.770 --> 28:04.310
Beijing Song and Dance Troupe.

28:04.310 --> 28:06.380
I'm auditioning for this troupe later.

28:06.380 --> 28:07.160
The main musician's role,

28:07.160 --> 28:08.290
with a solo!

28:10.960 --> 28:12.420
What do you mean by "sour"?

28:12.500 --> 28:14.320
No, not "sour."

28:14.440 --> 28:16.110
Solo.

28:16.370 --> 28:16.920
It means,

28:17.310 --> 28:18.380
in the middle of the

28:18.610 --> 28:19.410
performance,

28:19.500 --> 28:21.160
I have a segment all to myself.

28:21.610 --> 28:23.290
All the eyes will be on me.

28:23.290 --> 28:24.270
And all the lights

28:24.270 --> 28:26.290
will gather on me.

28:27.000 --> 28:27.960
It's dazzling.

28:38.810 --> 28:39.900
It's raining.

28:40.480 --> 28:42.610
You didn't bring an umbrella, did you?

28:44.660 --> 28:45.380
I did.

28:46.000 --> 28:46.960
Let's walk together.

28:46.960 --> 28:47.740
Wait for me.

29:06.750 --> 29:07.350
Dazzling.

29:10.850 --> 29:11.550
Thanks.

29:11.590 --> 29:12.520
You're welcome.

29:35.090 --> 29:35.620
If you...

29:36.480 --> 29:37.850
Have plans...

29:37.880 --> 29:38.590
I'm free.

29:40.240 --> 29:41.880
This is nice.

29:49.070 --> 29:50.140
Actually,

29:50.290 --> 29:52.010
I take the bus a lot

29:52.010 --> 29:53.670
to see the scenery in Beijing.

29:54.090 --> 29:55.390
Every time I look,

29:55.700 --> 29:57.230
I see a different side of it.

29:57.920 --> 29:59.580
Even though I'm from Beijing,

30:00.220 --> 30:01.440
I rarely

30:03.350 --> 30:04.750
get to know the city

30:05.140 --> 30:05.770
like this.

30:10.720 --> 30:12.820
You're actually quite different

30:13.270 --> 30:14.750
from what I imagined.

30:14.880 --> 30:16.410
So you've thought about me?

30:33.050 --> 30:34.250
Actually,

30:34.920 --> 30:37.050
I'm quite grateful for the rain today.

30:37.440 --> 30:39.770
Otherwise, I wouldn't have had the chance

30:40.700 --> 30:42.030
to let you get to know me.

30:45.310 --> 30:47.740
My family runs a restaurant.

30:49.010 --> 30:50.430
To be precise,

30:51.920 --> 30:53.050
it's a small diner.

30:54.420 --> 30:55.900
Back in high school,

30:56.380 --> 30:57.580
I was always fighting

30:57.680 --> 30:58.880
and causing trouble.

30:58.980 --> 31:00.010
Later, I don't know

31:00.010 --> 31:02.110
what wire in my brain

31:02.270 --> 31:03.000
got crossed,

31:03.010 --> 31:05.340
but I insisted on learning the saxophone.

31:07.720 --> 31:09.050
My family didn't agree.

31:10.110 --> 31:10.960
But one night,

31:10.960 --> 31:12.560
my mom went to the city center

31:13.330 --> 31:14.590
and brought this saxophone

31:14.590 --> 31:15.480
home for me.

31:16.270 --> 31:17.590
It was such a surprise.

31:21.330 --> 31:22.290
Your parents

31:23.550 --> 31:24.810
treat you really well.

31:24.920 --> 31:25.830
They really do.

31:26.440 --> 31:27.700
When there's a chance,

31:27.850 --> 31:29.110
I'll take you to my home

31:29.160 --> 31:29.830
for a meal.

31:36.720 --> 31:37.610
My dad

31:38.380 --> 31:39.910
worked in transportation.

31:41.880 --> 31:44.040
When I was in elementary school,

31:44.090 --> 31:45.700
my mom got pregnant again.

31:46.810 --> 31:47.830
To improve

31:47.830 --> 31:49.000
our family's life,

31:52.400 --> 31:54.730
my dad worked overtime driving every day.

31:58.330 --> 31:59.350
He

31:59.420 --> 32:01.480
never spent the night out.

32:03.030 --> 32:04.460
But on his way back one night,

32:04.460 --> 32:05.660
he had a car accident.

32:19.380 --> 32:21.040
To get from my home to Beijing,

32:21.530 --> 32:23.420
I have to take a bus for half an hour

32:23.420 --> 32:24.480
to the county town.

32:25.250 --> 32:26.740
Then I take a coach

32:26.740 --> 32:27.470
to Shanghai,

32:28.270 --> 32:30.500
and then take a train for over 10 hours

32:30.660 --> 32:32.120
to finally reach Beijing.

32:40.880 --> 32:41.830
You know what?

32:42.830 --> 32:44.880
It took me 22 years

32:45.900 --> 32:47.330
to see the scenery

32:49.420 --> 32:51.000
that is just a summer

32:51.000 --> 32:52.260
in your ordinary life.

33:39.750 --> 33:41.300
I called Director Ma

33:41.530 --> 33:42.660
and told him that

33:42.830 --> 33:45.270
the unopened bottle of liquor is authentic.

33:45.270 --> 33:46.590
What did Director Ma say?

33:46.590 --> 33:47.310
He said,

33:47.660 --> 33:49.000
let's just treat it as authentic.

33:49.000 --> 33:51.480
But that bottle is authentic.

33:51.480 --> 33:52.680
Your words mean nothing.

33:52.680 --> 33:54.680
It only works if Director Ma says it.

33:56.510 --> 33:57.190
Mr. Cui.

33:57.510 --> 33:59.240
I want to see Director Ma again.

33:59.570 --> 34:01.270
I want to explain it to him in person.

34:01.270 --> 34:02.840
Director Ma won't see you.

34:03.850 --> 34:04.910
Then what about...

34:05.460 --> 34:06.290
My role?

34:07.330 --> 34:08.170
Ranran,

34:08.440 --> 34:09.940
there are plenty of roles.

34:10.480 --> 34:11.380
Let's just wait.

34:11.380 --> 34:11.989
Okay?

34:15.530 --> 34:16.409
Mr. Cui.

34:16.780 --> 34:17.810
I'm begging you.

34:18.440 --> 34:19.710
I have things to do.

34:19.800 --> 34:20.699
I've got to go.

34:21.010 --> 34:21.880
Mr. Cui, I...

34:22.030 --> 34:22.960
I'm begging you.

34:23.070 --> 34:24.870
Just let me see Director Ma once.

34:24.940 --> 34:25.570
Just once.

34:25.570 --> 34:26.550
No, don't...

34:26.550 --> 34:27.210
Don't be like this.

34:27.210 --> 34:28.860
It looks bad if people see us like this.

34:28.860 --> 34:29.300
Look,

34:29.300 --> 34:31.630
Director Ma already said he won't see you.

34:32.380 --> 34:34.400
Then let me treat you to dinner, okay?

34:34.400 --> 34:36.300
It's not about a meal.

34:36.300 --> 34:37.670
Then we'll do 2, 3, even 4 meals.

34:37.670 --> 34:38.880
Do you take me for a glutton?

34:38.880 --> 34:40.380
Don't make this hard for me,

34:40.380 --> 34:41.130
okay?

34:45.320 --> 34:46.159
My money.

34:46.300 --> 34:47.150
Here, take this money.

34:47.150 --> 34:47.820
It's not much,

34:47.820 --> 34:48.480
but buy yourself some cigarettes.

34:48.480 --> 34:49.380
Why are you buying me cigarettes?

34:49.380 --> 34:50.500
What kind of person do you think I am?

34:50.500 --> 34:51.070
Take it.

34:51.130 --> 34:52.659
What do you take me for? I...

34:52.760 --> 34:53.780
I've never seen

34:53.780 --> 34:55.409
anyone as persistent as you.

34:56.380 --> 34:58.510
I really have no choice.

34:59.280 --> 35:00.710
No, no, don't cry.

35:00.840 --> 35:01.440
Don't cry.

35:01.630 --> 35:02.730
If someone I know sees us,

35:02.730 --> 35:04.210
they'd think I did something to you.

35:04.210 --> 35:04.570
I...

35:08.440 --> 35:09.760
Ranran, really.

35:11.000 --> 35:12.630
You must have been my mother in a past life.

35:12.630 --> 35:13.290
Seriously.

35:23.980 --> 35:25.380
Mr. Xu, is that a new bike?

35:26.860 --> 35:27.760
All the best with your business.

35:27.760 --> 35:28.300
Thanks.

35:30.120 --> 35:35.220
[Seasons Change Hotel]

35:34.530 --> 35:35.880
I was waiting inside for ages.

35:35.880 --> 35:36.840
And here you are.

35:39.650 --> 35:43.630
[Seasons Change Hotel]

35:40.050 --> 35:40.940
Where did you get this?

35:40.940 --> 35:41.880
I just bought it.

35:42.670 --> 35:43.620
You bought it?

35:44.570 --> 35:45.400
We can't keep borrowing a bike

35:45.400 --> 35:46.550
from Little Northeasterner every day.

35:46.550 --> 35:47.410
Besides, look,

35:47.500 --> 35:48.830
I cleared the back seat.

35:49.590 --> 35:52.520
You don't have to squeeze
onto the bus every day, now.

35:54.070 --> 35:56.330
You spent the money as soon as you made it.

35:56.420 --> 35:58.020
Isn't this more convenient?

35:58.920 --> 35:59.450
Let's go.

36:00.000 --> 36:00.530
Let's go.

36:00.940 --> 36:01.800
Then get on.

36:03.670 --> 36:04.130
Come on.

36:04.360 --> 36:05.150
Hold on tight.

36:05.150 --> 36:05.510
Okay.

36:05.780 --> 36:06.900
Here we go.

36:06.960 --> 36:07.620
Watch out.

36:08.980 --> 36:09.840
Zhuang Zhuang!

36:09.860 --> 36:10.440
Get down!

36:17.170 --> 36:18.410
Why are you here?

36:19.920 --> 36:21.380
It's early in the morning.

36:22.320 --> 36:23.450
Where are you going?

36:23.590 --> 36:24.630
Who is this?

36:26.260 --> 36:27.190
Hello, comrade.

36:27.480 --> 36:29.360
I'm Zhuang Zhuang's boyfriend.

36:35.170 --> 36:36.190
Kang Shunyin,

36:36.420 --> 36:37.620
don't talk nonsense.

36:40.090 --> 36:42.550
We're just missing a marriage certificate.

36:45.980 --> 36:46.720
You go ahead.

36:46.880 --> 36:48.080
I'll come over later.

36:56.690 --> 36:58.090
Who's the Argentina fan?

36:58.230 --> 36:59.030
A neighbor.

36:59.880 --> 37:00.410
Neigh...

37:00.610 --> 37:02.010
Morning, Zhuang Zhuang.

37:04.860 --> 37:05.920
Let's talk inside.

37:23.070 --> 37:23.880
This semi-basement...

37:23.880 --> 37:25.320
How can you live here?

37:25.630 --> 37:26.550
What's that smell?

37:26.550 --> 37:27.380
It stinks.

37:27.760 --> 37:29.400
Is this place even livable?

37:30.730 --> 37:32.260
How on earth did you find me?

37:34.000 --> 37:34.810
Don't forget,

37:35.590 --> 37:37.050
I'm the Chief of Security.

37:37.440 --> 37:38.480
You stalked me.

37:38.550 --> 37:39.610
How is it stalking?

37:40.260 --> 37:41.390
I'm protecting you.

37:41.670 --> 37:42.260
About us,

37:42.260 --> 37:43.760
didn't we clear that up long ago?

37:43.760 --> 37:44.960
You did make it clear.

37:45.550 --> 37:46.800
But I didn't agree.

37:48.090 --> 37:49.000
I'm serious about

37:49.000 --> 37:50.400
marrying you, okay?

37:50.480 --> 37:51.860
Look at you. This...

37:52.320 --> 37:52.880
Look at the place

37:52.880 --> 37:54.190
you're living in.

37:54.550 --> 37:55.810
It's like a rat's nest!

37:56.380 --> 37:56.900
Zhuang.

37:57.300 --> 37:58.710
Just come back to Wenzhou with me.

37:58.710 --> 38:00.260
The house is all ready for you.

38:00.260 --> 38:01.960
Stop making this hard for me, okay?

38:01.960 --> 38:03.070
How am I making it hard for you?

38:03.070 --> 38:05.070
You're the one making it hard for me.

38:10.400 --> 38:11.260
Zhuang Zhuang.

38:13.090 --> 38:13.530
You...

38:14.050 --> 38:15.440
Since you left,

38:15.800 --> 38:16.880
whenever I think of you all alone

38:16.880 --> 38:17.320
in Beijing,

38:17.320 --> 38:18.930
I get so panicked inside.

38:19.210 --> 38:20.590
I worry you're not eating well,

38:20.590 --> 38:21.590
or sleeping well,

38:21.630 --> 38:22.780
or that you'll run into

38:22.780 --> 38:24.040
neighbors in jerseys.

38:24.090 --> 38:25.490
What if they're bad guys?

38:27.420 --> 38:28.080
Seriously.

38:28.130 --> 38:29.480
How clearly do I have to say it

38:29.480 --> 38:31.080
for you to stop pestering me?

38:35.300 --> 38:35.780
Look.

38:36.500 --> 38:38.860
You look so beautiful sitting in the sunlight.

38:38.860 --> 38:40.400
I just love your beauty.

38:41.940 --> 38:42.610
Zhuang Zhuang.

38:42.610 --> 38:44.470
Just come back to Wenzhou with me.

38:44.800 --> 38:45.420
Once we're back,

38:45.420 --> 38:46.680
whatever you say goes.

38:46.840 --> 38:48.240
I'll listen to you, okay?

38:48.610 --> 38:49.120
Look.

38:49.710 --> 38:50.850
I came from Wenzhou.

38:51.210 --> 38:52.070
It's such a long way.

38:52.070 --> 38:52.710
Even if I didn't succeed,

38:52.710 --> 38:54.010
at least give me credit for trying.

38:54.010 --> 38:54.960
Not everyone has

38:55.460 --> 38:57.190
this kind of sincerity, right?

39:01.550 --> 39:03.010
We're engaged, after all.

39:03.420 --> 39:05.000
Gold bracelets, gold necklaces, and gold jewelry.

39:05.000 --> 39:05.760
I gave them all to you.

39:05.760 --> 39:06.480
You can't just say no

39:06.480 --> 39:07.280
and be done with it.

39:07.280 --> 39:08.380
That engagement was your family's

39:08.380 --> 39:10.030
own wishful thinking.

39:10.420 --> 39:11.360
Back then, we were just

39:11.360 --> 39:12.780
getting to know each other,

39:12.780 --> 39:13.440
weren't we?

39:13.530 --> 39:14.130
Who knew you would

39:14.130 --> 39:15.390
pull a stunt like that?

39:16.280 --> 39:17.710
Besides, the things were returned

39:17.710 --> 39:18.510
to you the way I received them.

39:18.510 --> 39:19.420
Don't tell me you didn't get them.

39:19.420 --> 39:20.000
But they still have

39:20.000 --> 39:21.060
your scent on them.

39:23.570 --> 39:24.170
I've never

39:24.260 --> 39:25.210
even touched them.

39:25.210 --> 39:26.670
How could there be a scent?

39:26.860 --> 39:27.720
Zhuang Zhuang.

39:30.320 --> 39:31.460
I'm trying to be patient

39:31.460 --> 39:32.130
talking to you.

39:32.130 --> 39:32.670
Don't...

39:34.130 --> 39:35.330
Don't push me too far.

39:36.510 --> 39:37.440
What do you want?

39:42.380 --> 39:44.440
You came to Beijing to find Mr. Zheng.

39:44.590 --> 39:46.450
My family introduced you, right?

39:46.530 --> 39:47.230
If it weren't for my family,

39:47.230 --> 39:48.190
would you be in Beijing?

39:48.190 --> 39:48.860
Don't burn your bridges

39:48.860 --> 39:49.860
now that you're in Beijing.

39:49.860 --> 39:50.860
Yes, yes.

39:50.860 --> 39:52.380
I am grateful to your family.

39:52.380 --> 39:53.860
I am grateful to your parents, too.

39:53.860 --> 39:54.510
I am grateful that they

39:54.510 --> 39:56.040
introduced Mr. Zheng to me.

39:56.380 --> 39:57.460
But to thank you,

39:57.480 --> 39:58.300
didn't my mom help your family's factory

39:58.300 --> 39:59.150
a lot too?

40:00.300 --> 40:01.630
When I first met Mr. Zheng,

40:01.630 --> 40:03.090
you were there too, right?

40:03.230 --> 40:04.340
Mr. Zheng said

40:04.510 --> 40:06.150
many people introduce students to him,

40:06.150 --> 40:07.440
but he doesn't accept just anyone.

40:07.440 --> 40:08.130
Right?

40:09.360 --> 40:10.730
Wasn't it after he met me

40:10.760 --> 40:11.690
and heard me sing

40:11.690 --> 40:13.260
that he thought I had potential,

40:13.260 --> 40:14.420
hoped I could succeed,

40:14.420 --> 40:15.320
and therefore accepted me?

40:15.320 --> 40:16.020
Right?

40:16.510 --> 40:17.570
I'm not wrong, am I?

40:18.880 --> 40:19.530
Yes, yes.

40:19.610 --> 40:20.880
It was your family's influence.

40:20.880 --> 40:22.140
But I paid the tuition.

40:22.230 --> 40:22.880
I didn't pay

40:22.880 --> 40:23.670
a penny less.

40:24.820 --> 40:25.320
Kang Shunyin.

40:25.320 --> 40:26.420
Don't think you can use this

40:26.420 --> 40:27.620
to threaten me again.

40:28.090 --> 40:28.920
Ridiculous.

40:34.880 --> 40:35.740
Zhuang Zhuang.

40:36.150 --> 40:36.820
I've noticed that

40:36.820 --> 40:37.420
after coming to Beijing,

40:37.420 --> 40:38.620
you've changed a bit.

40:41.800 --> 40:43.400
Are you seeing someone else?

40:44.360 --> 40:45.890
Is it that guy in the jersey?

40:46.400 --> 40:47.000
What's so great

40:47.000 --> 40:48.050
about someone with a bike?

40:48.050 --> 40:49.380
I'll buy you a car, okay?

40:49.530 --> 40:50.630
I'll get you whatever car you want.

40:50.630 --> 40:51.130
Get out.

40:51.380 --> 40:52.420
How about a Polonaise?

40:52.420 --> 40:53.010
Get out.

40:53.050 --> 40:53.980
I'm not leaving.

40:54.670 --> 40:55.590
-What are you doing?
-Get out!

40:55.590 --> 40:56.340
I'm not leaving!

40:56.340 --> 40:57.010
Have you no shame?

40:56.420 --> 41:03.160
[119 Firefighter Hotline]

40:57.030 --> 40:58.110
-Get out.
-I won’t.

40:58.110 --> 40:58.480
Get out!

40:58.480 --> 40:58.940
What's going on?

40:58.940 --> 40:59.670
What are you doing? I'm not leaving.

40:59.670 --> 41:00.170
What are you doing?

41:00.170 --> 41:01.050
You're hurting my waist.

41:01.050 --> 41:02.940
That sounds like Zhuang Zhuang.

41:03.050 --> 41:03.670
I won't leave.

41:03.670 --> 41:05.170
Didn't Zhuang Zhuang go with Shengli

41:05.170 --> 41:06.150
to sell clothes?

41:06.150 --> 41:06.630
Get out!

41:06.900 --> 41:07.450
Yeah.

41:07.730 --> 41:08.800
Zhuang Zhuang, what are you doing?

41:08.720 --> 41:09.520
[119 Firefighter Hotline]

41:08.800 --> 41:10.320
Don't! Don't! What are you doing?

41:10.320 --> 41:11.130
Why are you pushing me?

41:11.130 --> 41:13.000
No. Zhuang Zhuang, open the door.

41:13.670 --> 41:14.110
You...

41:14.190 --> 41:15.610
You have a great advantage here,

41:15.610 --> 41:16.280
but you're favoring a toad,

41:16.280 --> 41:17.860
and you won't let me say anything?

41:17.860 --> 41:19.130
I'm telling you, Zhuang Zhuang.

41:19.130 --> 41:20.460
Don't think I don't know

41:20.500 --> 41:21.960
what twisted guts that guy

41:22.010 --> 41:22.610
in the Argentina jersey

41:22.610 --> 41:23.810
hides in his belly.

41:24.090 --> 41:24.880
One day, I'll rip them out

41:24.880 --> 41:26.080
and cook them for you.

41:28.960 --> 41:29.690
I'm sorry.

41:30.260 --> 41:31.130
I'm really sorry.

41:31.130 --> 41:32.230
Sorry for

41:32.670 --> 41:33.320
the noise.

41:33.420 --> 41:34.070
Here.

41:34.400 --> 41:35.130
Have a smoke.

41:35.320 --> 41:36.520
Please, have a smoke.

41:36.650 --> 41:37.010
I...

41:37.230 --> 41:39.050
I'm Zhuang Zhuang's fiancé.

41:39.150 --> 41:40.550
Sorry to disturb your rest.

41:40.550 --> 41:41.190
Please, have a smoke.

41:41.190 --> 41:41.860
Have a smoke.

41:41.860 --> 41:42.920
I'm truly sorry.

41:43.010 --> 41:43.850
Sorry. Here.

41:43.900 --> 41:45.600
Let me make it up to you.

41:46.210 --> 41:47.690
I'm really sorry.

41:47.690 --> 41:48.760
Here, have a smoke.

41:48.900 --> 41:50.010
It's okay, take it for someone else.

41:50.010 --> 41:50.820
Give it to someone else.

41:50.820 --> 41:52.260
In the future, Zhuang Zhuang

41:52.260 --> 41:53.340
may trouble you all again.

41:53.340 --> 41:54.460
When the time comes,

41:54.460 --> 41:55.360
please look out for her.

41:55.360 --> 41:56.400
Please look out for her.

41:56.400 --> 41:56.840
Here.

41:57.000 --> 41:57.730
Have a smoke.

41:59.460 --> 42:00.630
I'm off to work.

42:02.030 --> 42:03.550
What a strange guy.

42:03.550 --> 42:04.480
Here, handsome.

42:04.510 --> 42:05.240
Have a smoke.

42:05.650 --> 42:06.310
Who are you?

42:06.860 --> 42:09.380
I... I'm Zhuang Zhuang's fiancé.

42:09.530 --> 42:10.360
In the future,

42:10.460 --> 42:11.630
please take care of Zhuang Zhuang.

42:11.630 --> 42:12.320
Have a smoke.

42:12.320 --> 42:14.050
What do you mean, cook his guts?

42:14.760 --> 42:16.490
You think you're making a stew?

42:20.780 --> 42:22.310
The people living here

42:23.110 --> 42:24.010
are so strange.

42:27.820 --> 42:30.500
A butterfly flies in...

42:30.510 --> 42:30.920
Ma'am.

42:31.380 --> 42:31.920
You scared me.

42:31.920 --> 42:33.070
In the Wenzhou dialect,

42:33.070 --> 42:34.400
what does "linsi" mean?

42:36.130 --> 42:37.070
"Linsi"?

42:37.150 --> 42:39.170
Lin... Linsi... si.

42:39.920 --> 42:40.820
Neighbor.

42:41.530 --> 42:42.300
Neighbor.

42:42.570 --> 42:43.280
Neighbor?

42:47.800 --> 42:49.500
Do you have a neighbor from Wenzhou?

42:49.500 --> 42:50.310
I have to say,

42:50.610 --> 42:51.670
we Wenzhou people are amazing.

42:51.670 --> 42:53.330
Zhuang Zhuang is my neighbor.

42:54.690 --> 42:55.230
Xu.

42:55.230 --> 42:56.480
How did Zhuang Zhuang become your neighbor?

42:56.480 --> 42:57.730
Did you two have a fight?
